    "1250": {
      "review_count": 17,
      "average_rating": 4.41,
      "html": "<div id=\"tab-reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--reviews panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div id=\"reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Reviews\"><div id=\"comments\"><h2 class=\"woocommerce-Reviews-title\">17 reviews for <span>Vyntech Ultimate Mega Combo</span></h2><ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1101\">\n<div id=\"comment-1101\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11a?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Rohit Khandelwal</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Bhai kya mast combo hai! 7 straps ke saath har din naya look milta hai. Watch display is very smooth and pods audio quality is surprisingly good with decent bass.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/44-i20-ultra-smart-watch-combo-7in1-h22-android-ios-mahitek-yes-original-imahhqgvey7se5pv.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1102\">\n<div id=\"comment-1102\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11b?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Anjali Nair</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Total value for money. The watch pairs easily with my phone and fitness tracking works well. Earbuds battery could be a little better, lasts around 5 hours on full volume.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_8ca493836bf4437e96b221b2d380fd8e.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1103\">\n<div id=\"comment-1103\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11c?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Amit Singh</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Here is my own review for this product: what I found. Initially my pods were not syncing with each other. The front-line support was busy, so I emailed the head contact help.vyntech@gmail.com. They replied in 15 mins with a reset trick and it worked perfectly! Love the escalation support. Premium quality combo.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1104\">\n<div id=\"comment-1104\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11d?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Gaurav Patil</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Watch looks very premium but pedometer shows some extra steps while I am driving my car. Pods are good.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Gaurav,<br><br>We apologize for the tracking inconsistency. Bumpy car rides can sometimes trigger the step sensors. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and we will assist you in updating the firmware, which includes better motion-calibration algorithms to prevent false steps.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1105\">\n<div id=\"comment-1105\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11e?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Karthikeyan</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Romba nalla product. 7 straps are amazing, completely changes the watch style. Earbuds fit perfectly and audio is crisp.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_15ed4755d1904d0997f3c7646e7f447f.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1106\">\n<div id=\"comment-1106\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11f?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Priya Sharma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>The ultimate gift package! Bought it for my brother's birthday and he loved it. Unbelievable price for a premium looking watch + pods + 7 straps.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_ad1bf7aaa12a4fe1aa8d674e127b7fa9.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1107\">\n<div id=\"comment-1107\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11g?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 2 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:40%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">2</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Varun Das</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Watch is working fine but initiated a replacement because the left pod is not charging inside the case properly.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Varun,<br><br>We really apologize for the inconvenience caused by the defective pod. You need not worry, your replacement request has been approved. A brand new sealed combo will be delivered to you at the time of pickup.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1108\">\n<div id=\"comment-1108\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11h?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Venkatesh Rao</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Chala bagundi. Watch display is very bright outdoors. Premium quality for this price.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_d16c44362baf43eeb19be18207dbff22.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1109\">\n<div id=\"comment-1109\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11i?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Mohit Desai</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Delivery was delayed by almost 3 days, maybe courier fault. But the package arrived safely without dents. Both watch and pods are working smoothly.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_d2286f13ebb24900a46d10d55d6a08e3.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1110\">\n<div id=\"comment-1110\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11j?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Aditya S.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Display is super bright even in direct sunlight. Calling works perfectly on both watch and pods. Hands down the best combo available.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1111\">\n<div id=\"comment-1111\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11k?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Tarun Kumar</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Watch speaker volume is a bit low in traffic. Pods audio is good but ENC is very basic for outdoor calls.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Tarun,<br><br>We apologize for the inconvenience during calls. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our product expert will assist you in updating the firmware for both devices, which significantly improves mic sensitivity and speaker volume.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1112\">\n<div id=\"comment-1112\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11l?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sumit Yadav</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Ek number combo bhai. Airpods audio quality is surprisingly good and watch touch response is flagship level.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1113\">\n<div id=\"comment-1113\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11m?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Neha Patil</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Watch syncs easily with my iPhone without any connection drops. App interface is decent.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1114\">\n<div id=\"comment-1114\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11n?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Kunal T.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Super combo. Using the metal strap for office and silicone ones for gym. Both devices holding up well.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1115\">\n<div id=\"comment-1115\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11o?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Deepak Joshi</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Very nice product received. Worth the money. Fast delivery by Vyntech.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1116\">\n<div id=\"comment-1116\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11p?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Manish Reddy</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Best combo on the internet. Box packing was very premium, perfect for gifting.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1117\">\n<div id=\"comment-1117\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/11q?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Arjun P.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Fully satisfied with the purchase. Excellent value.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n</ol></div><div class=\"clear\"></div></div></div>"
